# xSPECTRE Agent Installation Guide - macOS
# Version: 1.0.0

This is the macOS installer package for xSPECTRE Agent v1.0.0

## Installation Instructions

1. Double-click the xspectre-agent-1.0.0.dmg file to mount the disk image

2. Follow the installation wizard steps:
   - Review the license agreement
   - Select installation destination (usually Macintosh HD)
   - Enter your administrator password when prompted

3. Launch the xSPECTRE Agent:
   - Open Applications > Utilities > xSPECTRE Agent
   - Or use Spotlight search to find "xSPECTRE Agent"

4. In the agent settings, enter your enrollment key from the xSPECTRE Ops Console

5. The agent will appear in your menu bar and automatically connect to the console

## System Requirements
- macOS 10.12 (Sierra) or later
- Intel or Apple Silicon processor
- Administrator privileges for installation
- Network connectivity to the console server

